      <title>伦敦交易所在推出加密货币之前失去了一半的 ETF 团队</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/london-exchange-loses-half-of-etf-team-ahead-of-crypto-launch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在伦敦证券交易所集团有限公司准备上市首批与加密货币相关的产品时，该公司负责交易所交易基金的四人团队失去了一半。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-24/london-exchange-loses-half-of-etf-team-ahead-of-crypto-launch</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 May 2024 08:58:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
